Mr. Martin, Cat.

05:59.544 --> 06:01.063
Thank you for coming.

06:02.773 --> 06:04.447
Please, sit down.

06:10.118 --> 06:12.696
This couldn't happen at a worse time.

06:12.816 --> 06:14.564
I'm 24 hours

06:14.564 --> 06:17.500
from a three billion dollar
takeover of Franken Bear.

06:17.509 --> 06:19.787
Otherwise, I would go to Mauritania myself.

06:19.907 --> 06:22.272
Not a good idea, crossing
the local warlord.

06:22.392 --> 06:23.192
No...

06:23.208 --> 06:24.642
But not unlike Zac.

06:24.644 --> 06:25.695
My...

06:25.715 --> 06:28.019
My son means well, but...

06:28.285 --> 06:30.165
he's strong-willed, to say the least.

06:30.195 --> 06:31.833
Who contacted you?

06:32.070 --> 06:34.860
A local man by the name of Ayoob.

06:34.980 --> 06:36.561
Did he say where we could find him?

06:36.571 --> 06:37.275
No.

06:37.395 --> 06:40.586
It was just that Zac was
begging for me to get help.

06:40.706 --> 06:43.293
And also that somehow he's been wounded.

06:43.413 --> 06:44.656
Wounded?

06:45.936 --> 06:47.372
I think he's been shot.

06:50.573 --> 06:52.286
It's a remote area.

06:52.302 --> 06:53.866
A Westerner looking for your son

06:53.884 --> 06:55.787
would quickly become a target as well.

06:55.787 --> 06:57.149
I understand that.

06:58.457 --> 07:01.320
But Cat tells me you're
the best at what you do.

07:04.896 --> 07:07.356
I will pay any fee you ask.

07:07.383 --> 07:09.037
I'm sure you could afford it.

07:10.429 --> 07:12.387
But I'm not sure success is possible.

07:12.408 --> 07:13.557
What you need is an airlift.

07:13.585 --> 07:16.420
I have had the Embassy
on the phone non-stop.

07:16.439 --> 07:18.424
They say it's simply not an option.

07:22.960 --> 07:26.755
This is the first time
since he was a teenager

07:27.469 --> 07:29.911
Zac has asked me for anything.

07:32.399 --> 07:34.428
Please, Mr. Martin...

07:39.901 --> 07:41.216
Bring him home.

07:44.627 --> 07:46.438
And if he's already dead?

07:51.461 --> 07:53.665
Bring him home anyway.

07:57.781 --> 07:59.333
What's your connection?

07:59.373 --> 08:01.211
The father or the son?

08:02.373 --> 08:05.044
I dated Zac when I was stationed in Jordan.

08:05.059 --> 08:06.708
It was a long time ago.

08:06.745 --> 08:08.394
I'm sorry, I should've told you.

08:08.596 --> 08:09.726
Why didn't you?

08:09.744 --> 08:11.848
I didn't want you to feel obligated.

08:13.622 --> 08:15.525
Are you going to do it?

08:20.546 --> 08:23.143
I'm gonna need you with me.

