09:45.289 --> 09:47.271
Awfully quiet, isn't it?

09:48.250 --> 09:49.905
A ghost town.

10:29.325 --> 10:31.080
I counted 19 beds.

10:31.200 --> 10:33.386
Nineteen empty beds.

10:33.506 --> 10:35.819
Wherever they went, they left in a hurry.

10:40.465 --> 10:42.441
He was gone before the shooting started.

10:42.468 --> 10:43.659
How do you know?

10:43.779 --> 10:45.279
More bullet holes,

10:45.587 --> 10:47.389
and there's no blood here.

10:47.965 --> 10:51.085
What kind of a man shoots
through a closed door?

10:51.720 --> 10:53.591
The kind who shoots first and

10:53.622 --> 10:55.566
asks questions later.

10:58.660 --> 11:00.261
There's Zac.

11:06.926 --> 11:08.115
You OK?

11:09.359 --> 11:10.621
I'm OK.

11:27.021 --> 11:28.264
Tell me more.

11:28.292 --> 11:30.390
- About?
- Zac.

11:30.606 --> 11:33.094
If he's the package, I need his dimensions.

11:34.027 --> 11:35.865
Hard-charging.

11:35.911 --> 11:37.863
Can't sit still.

11:38.344 --> 11:40.481
Thinks he's the smartest
guy in the room and

11:40.502 --> 11:41.902
totally believes in his cause.

11:43.737 --> 11:45.386
Look.

11:51.711 --> 11:53.512
Bullet holes.

11:53.632 --> 11:55.932
Looks like it was forced off the road.

12:18.638 --> 12:20.699
Radiator took a hit.

12:24.669 --> 12:26.086
Frank!

12:29.827 --> 12:31.235
Hiding place?

12:33.285 --> 12:35.553
Maybe not a good one.

12:35.854 --> 12:38.360
If that was your friend,
he lost a lot of blood.

12:58.376 --> 13:00.585
