13:01.212 --> 13:02.913
We're looking for a friend.

13:03.114 --> 13:05.277
He was hurt three nights ago.

13:07.551 --> 13:09.375
Put that away...

13:09.495 --> 13:11.076
and come with me.

13:13.199 --> 13:15.696
What the hell do you think you are doing?

13:16.610 --> 13:18.220
We told you.

13:18.340 --> 13:21.101
- We're looking for Zac Preston.
- My guess is he's dead.

13:21.120 --> 13:23.132
And you will be soon, if you don't leave.

13:23.159 --> 13:24.997
We found a bus that was shot up.

13:25.015 --> 13:27.036
Blood in the luggage compartment.

13:27.960 --> 13:30.603
- Did you treat him, Doctor?
- Zac was a friend.

13:30.631 --> 13:32.589
But Al-Harazi made it clear.

13:32.709 --> 13:35.232
He will kill anyone who helps him.

13:35.352 --> 13:36.951
Your friend gets shot

13:37.071 --> 13:38.607
and you send him away?

13:38.634 --> 13:40.509
This isn't about friendship.

13:40.629 --> 13:44.222
I am the only doctor for 100 kilometers.

13:44.342 --> 13:46.720
People need me alive.

13:47.590 --> 13:50.224
Now go. And don't come back!

13:52.762 --> 13:54.262
Heart-warming.

13:54.464 --> 13:56.754
At least we know where Zac isn't.

13:59.368 --> 14:01.272
Can I see that picture again?

14:04.440 --> 14:06.147
That's the same guy, isn't it?

14:06.175 --> 14:08.232
Standing next to Zac?

14:19.803 --> 14:21.266
Speak English?

14:22.529 --> 14:23.580
A little.

14:23.758 --> 14:25.090
What's your name?

14:25.913 --> 14:27.120
Ayoob.

14:27.166 --> 14:29.398
Ayoob, you called Zac's father.

14:29.416 --> 14:31.611
He sent us. We're here to get him.

14:34.886 --> 14:37.090
This isn't his grave, is it?

14:39.523 --> 14:41.032
It's a cousin's...

14:41.343 --> 14:44.197
killed by al-Hazari for helping Zac.

14:44.435 --> 14:47.087
Tell us where he is. Then we'll go.

14:51.166 --> 14:52.831
He says not to trust you.

14:52.858 --> 14:54.459
I know what he says.

14:55.978 --> 14:57.615
Take this to Zac.

14:57.735 --> 14:59.462
It'll prove I'm a friend.

15:07.144 --> 15:09.495
Sayed will take you to a safe place.

15:09.733 --> 15:11.301
You wait there.

