So, what are you going to do?

17:36.200 --> 17:38.194
Shoot Zac in cold blood?

17:39.128 --> 17:40.461
Killing an aid worker

17:40.463 --> 17:42.192
will make you more famous
than you want to be.

17:42.312 --> 17:43.673
An aid worker?

17:44.251 --> 17:46.234
Is that what you think he is?

17:46.587 --> 17:48.255
Zac Preston is a thief.

17:48.292 --> 17:49.572
What did he steal?

17:51.024 --> 17:52.524
It doesn't matter.

17:52.746 --> 17:54.760
What matters is that it was mine.

